Shared decision-making for the treatment of proximal femoral fractures in frail 
institutionalised older patients: healthcare providers' perceived barriers and 
facilitators.

Spronk I(1), Loggers SAI(2)(3), Joosse P(2), Willems HC(4), Van Balen R(5), 
Gosens T(6), Ponsen KJ(2)(7), Steens J(8), Van de Ree CLP(9), Zuurmond RG(10), 
